task.summary: Finished up the low level working. Added a static AuthQueMgr ref to comms now removes itself whenever an exception occurs or whenever a disconnect message is sent by the user. Code needs to be cleaned ie replace literals with constants. Also added a Group class which holds FileLister. Group requires a ThreadNotifier which is passed onto FileLister. FileWatcher now fires a callback whenever a file is removed/added so that the list can be changed. Will clean code by next commit
